OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with a few showers
OL,7,Falong the coast. Showery outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain then pushing across the region
OL,9,Fovernight, clearing eastwards for most
OL,10,Fby dawn. Frost-free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy start with showery
OL,13,Frain soon clearing. Turning brighter
OL,14,Fbehind with sunny spells but also
OL,15,Fshowers by the afternoon in the east,
OL,16,Fpossibly heavy and thundery. Feeling
OL,17,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
