OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FCloudier but warmer on Saturday with
OL,7,Fshowery rain in the south by the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Drier and breezier through
OL,9,FSunday and Monday with showers
OL,10,Farriving later. Turning cooler.
